Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Hotels for the homeless
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xqhc
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Aug 1986
New York mayor to look at suggestion to house the city's homeless in empty hotel rooms. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less